unnormalised: Arrey yaar, tuje KYC update keley pan number ani IFSC code ghalun? SBI magta asa soglleank 31/12 meren korunk na zalear account block zatlo!
normalised: Arrey yaar, tunvem tuje K-Y-C tuje P-A-N number ani I-F-S-C code dita update kelem? S-B-I soglleank te vattis december poriant korunk sangta na zalear account block zatlem!
